<h2 id="evaluating-the-expression">Evaluating the Expression <a class="headerlink" href="evaluating-expression#evaluating-the-expression" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Refresh the browser again. Things look good! Time to evaluate the expression.</p>
<p>To use the expression language, we just need to create an <code>ExpressionLanguage</code> object.
