<p>Ok, back to the browser. There it is! How about our test?</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./bin/phpunit -c app --filter testGETProgrammer</div></code></pre>
<p>Hey, they're passing too! Amazing!</p>
<p>In just a few short minutes, we made an entirely reusable linking system. I will
admit that this idea was stolen from a library called <a href="https://github.com/willdurand/Hateoas">Hateoas</a>. Now, don't
you feel dangerous?</p>

    
